<div class="title">Irregular Heartbeat</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Tuscani&Exact=1">Tuscani</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Tuscani. "Irregular Heartbeat: An Experience with Caffeine (exp18257)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 17, 2002. erowid.org/exp/18257</div>

